com.streakapi.crm.datatype

Class Box

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.streakapi.crm.datatype.Box

  • public class Box
extends java.lang.Object
    The Box object contains the following information about a Box in Streak.
  • pipelineKey
  • creatorKey
  • creationTimestamp (in dd-MM-yyyy, HH:00:00 format)
  • lastUpdatedTimestamp (in dd-MM-yyyy, HH:00:00 format)
  • name
  • notes
  • stageKey
  • fields
  • followerKeys
  • followerCount
  • commentCount
  • reminderCount
  • gmailThreadCount
  • fileCount
  • boxKey
  • key
  • otherItemsMap (Contains a Map of other items from Streak API that are not listed above)
Author:
dineshkp
See Also:
https://www.streak.com/api/
